donde $\Delta t = \frac{\sqrt{R^2 + R'^2}}{c}$.

**Velocidad Circular Efectiva:**
$$v_c^2(R) = R \frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial R} \approx \frac{GM(<R)}{R} \left(1 + \alpha \frac{R}{R_0}\right)$$

